Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You too, Kalifa!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.00,0:09:36.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You haven't learned your lesson \Nand are wearing such outrageous clothes again!}Haven't you learned by now \Nyou can't wear such scandalous clothes?!
