Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, that's it. Let's open the door \Nand go inside already.}{Um}Well, that was fun.\NLet's open the {door}gate and head inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.70,0:10:05.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, what a huge door! \NAnd this requires manual operation?}Hard to believe the size of this {door}gate!\NAnd it's manually operated?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Can those two {weirdos}freaks open it by themselves?
