Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.29,0:10:16.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... }Um, each dock has only \Nfive shipwright foremen.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.28,0:10:20.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They may not look like it, but their skills made them foremen at Dock 1.}Strange as they are, their skills earned\Nthem {a spot}their spots as Dock {1}One foremen.
