Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a world where craftsmen's \Nskills are all that matters.}In this {world}industry,\Nwhat matters is how one plies their trade.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if their personalities are weird, \Ndon't worry about it.}They're {weird}freaky, but so what?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, {they're}they {\i1}are{\i0} {weird}freaky.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah, the door's started opening.}Ah! It's starting to open!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.57,0:10:36.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let the money leave your hands. \NI don't think we have thieves inside, but...}And keep hold of your money.\NThere shouldn't be thieves here, but still.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, it was also my fault earlier, \Nand it caused you trouble, too.}Well, it's partially my fault. \NSorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hey, Luffy! \N– Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Make sure you guard me good!
