Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whoooa! {Huge}It's all huge!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A shipyard has a tremendous impact \Nwhen seen up close!}This shipyard's even more incredible \Nwhen seen up close!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yeah! \N– True!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh? They're building a huge galleon! \N{Whose is that?}Who's it for?
