Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, this way.}Come! This way.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs10} {\r}!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey! The boss is here!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs10} {\r}!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
