Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll come by later!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good day}Nice day today, Iceburg-{\i1}san{\fs10} {\r}!{\fs\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... Hello, are things going well?}Um, hi there. Everything going well?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! They're going pretty well!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whoa! {Ice pops is quite popular.}Everyone likes Iceboss.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.46,0:12:04.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course he is. In this city, \Nskills are all that matters.}Indeed they do. \NSkill means everything in this city.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.23,0:12:09.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{On this island, shipbuilding \Nwas well-developed from the start,}Shipbuilding has always been \Nthis island's main industry,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and seven shipbuilding companies \Nwere competing with each other.}and seven shipyards were \Ncompeting for contracts.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.22,0:12:17.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Meanwhile, he attracted craftsmen \Nwith his genius shipbuilding skills.}He eventually charmed the shipwrights \Nwith his genius craftsmanship.
