Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.09,0:12:59.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.90,0:13:04.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We came to this island in order to have our ship repaired and to find a new crew member.}We came to this island to get\Nour ship fixed and find a new crew member.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's true that we have {tons}a whole slew of shipwrights,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I wonder if anyone would \Nwant to go on board a pirate ship.}but I wonder if any fancy the life of a pirate.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.47,0:13:14.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you find someone who wants to go \Nwith you, you can headhunt him.}If there's anyone here who's willing \Nto sail with you, they're yours.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.23,0:13:19.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Really?! You're {}pretty generous! \N{Can't I ask you to join us, pops}How about you, old guy?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... I can't. I'm the mayor.}Um, I can't. I'm the mayor.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who cares?!}Blow it off!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.67,0:13:30.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, is the woman named \NNico Robin really on board your ship?}By the way, is there a woman \Nnamed Nico Robin on your ship?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, she is.}There is! She's really smart.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What? Is something the matter with Robin?
