Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Keep that steady! Don't rush! Go slowly!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.35,0:13:56.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If we could install a cannon like that, \N{the Merry would also be... Hm?}the Merry would be more– Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whoa! A demi-culverin{}{cannon}!{No need for "cannon," as "culverin" already refers to a cannon. We also don't need to hand-hold, as it's on screen. -gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.44,0:14:04.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How cool! It's so long...! And shining!}So cool! It's so long... and shiny!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna fire something like that, one time!}I'd give anything to fire \Nsomething like that {one time}just once.
