Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'd let me try firing it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.08,0:14:20.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait. We've now got 300 million belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We should be able to buy\None or more cannons like that!}We can afford to buy a few of those cannons!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wasn't there someone there?}Wasn't someone standing there?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kaku!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Where have you been? \N– An assessment.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're the guy from earlier! \NSo you checked our ship?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I did.}Right you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you were here, Iceburg-san.}Oh, Iceburg-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're present.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know the situation. How was it?}I'm all caught up. How did it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well...}In all honesty...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Come {down now}on down!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.28,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true?!
