Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.57,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{I never lie on the job.}A lie has no legs in my line of work.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? Where's}So, where's Usopp?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.61,0:15:54.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was wandering about over there up \Nuntil just a moment ago.}He {\i1}was{\i0} just over there up until a moment ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.51,0:16:01.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! \NDon't these {bags}cases belong to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahh! {They're the bags Usopp was carrying!}Usopp was carrying these!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're ours.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.29,0:16:14.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... Where did Usopp go... \Nleaving our precious money alone?!}C'mon! Where did you go, Usopp, \Nleaving all our precious money unattended?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Those bags hold 200 million belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,200 million belly?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way}Not possible. See ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So, how much {does it look like it'll cost}will it cost?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We can pay as much as you like! \NWe've got tons of money!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.47,0:16:41.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like her to be stronger, \Nhave more cannons, and be faster!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you also add pretty \Ndecorations on the outer panels?}Can you also stylize the outer hull \Nwith some tasteful engravings?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you renovate inside as well?}{I'd like the interior renovated as well.}Could you renovate the interior as well?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, hold on a sec...}Just hold your horses.
