Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.05,0:17:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Frankly speaking, your ship...}I'll give it to you straight.\NYour ship...
