Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's {taken a lot of damage}more or less kaput.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no...}No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But we've been traveling \Njust fine up until today!
