Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The probability {of her reaching the next island is...}that she reaches the next island is...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,zero.
