Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{sail anymore?}done sailing?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Crap...}Well, crap.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.99,0:18:31.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Sanji. \NI was so focused on books that...}I'm sorry, Sanji.\NI got a little {preoccupied with}lost in the books.
