Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.50,0:22:03.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{without a doubt, the ones who would feel \Nthat it's a totally different ship...}without a doubt, the crew who knew the old ship best would instantly feel the difference.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{would be you guys! Coo coo!}That crew'd be {\i1}you{\i0} guys!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no...}So, that...
