Dialogue: 5,0:27:15.85,0:27:17.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's an abduction!}They {abducted}kidnapped him!{To match the new title -gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:17.57,0:27:19.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! {We'll go look for him right away!}We need to find him quickly!
