Dialogue: 5,0:36:04.89,0:36:11.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We have to... have our ship repaired.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:14.48,0:36:17.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That money is crucial to us!}We desperately need that money!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:21.49,0:36:25.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,With that money, we can finally...
Dialogue: 5,0:36:25.08,0:36:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can finally repair the Going Merry's scars!}We can finally mend \Nthe Going Merry's wounds!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:30.62,0:36:35.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't let you jerks have it!}This money... I won't let you assholes take it!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:41.68,0:36:43.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you so worked up about?}What's got you all worked up?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:44.50,0:36:48.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like you love your ship quite a bit.}I see you really love your ship, am I right?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:48.19,0:36:52.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, no matter what happens to your ship,}Too bad! Whatever happens to your ship,
Dialogue: 5,0:36:52.64,0:36:56.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{this money is already ours.}this money belongs to {\i1}us{\i0} now.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:58.52,0:37:04.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, {no matter what we steal \Nfrom pirates, }no one considers stealing from pirates{we won't be accused of committing a crime.}{no one will consider it} a crime.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:04.09,0:37:07.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is dirty money that you stole \Nfrom somewhere anyway, right?}Let me guess!\NIt's dirty money you stole{ in the first place}, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:37:09.00,0:37:11.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, let us have it.}So, just let us keep it.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:13.21,0:37:16.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you like, try begging the Navy for help.}You could always beg the Navy for help.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:16.67,0:37:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys are the ones who'll be captured.}But you'll probably be the ones arrested.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:20.81,0:37:23.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Too bad for Straw Hat Luffy...}It's a shame that Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:37:23.61,0:37:29.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that he has a useless underling \Nwho can't even watch over money.}has such a useless underling \Nwho can't even guard his money.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:37.10,0:37:41.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys, have some fun with him later.}Guys, go ahead and show him a good time.
Dialogue: 5,0:37:42.57,0:37:47.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna take this money \Nand go shopping at once.}Right now, I'm gonna take\Nthis money out for a little shopping!
Dialogue: 5,0:37:48.06,0:37:49.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is gonna be great!}I can't wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:37:49.53,0:37:50.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold it}Not so fast!
Dialogue: 5,0:37:50.49,0:37:53.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal{:} Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:00.75,0:38:05.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Remember this, long-nosed boy. \NMy name is Franky.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:05.72,0:38:11.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If you want to leave this town alive, \N{you shouldn't cross me.}you'd be wise not to cross me.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:14.60,0:38:18.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What... What're you doing?! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:22.51,0:38:26.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Such a pathetic weapon wouldn't work on us.}Puny weapons like this won't work on us!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:26.95,0:38:29.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,See ya, long-nose.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:29.28,0:38:32.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the 200 million belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:32.79,0:38:36.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold it}Stop! Give it back... to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:36.10,0:38:37.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:38.10,0:38:39.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Give it baaack!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:49.29,0:38:50.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Give it... back.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:50.97,0:38:53.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Give it... baaack!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:05.44,0:39:08.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Give...{.} it... back!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:10.87,0:39:15.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Give it baaaaaack!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:24.73,0:39:27.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I just have to hold out until Robin comes back.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:30.43,0:39:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll only become a burden to them \Nif I march in with them.}I'd just get in the way\Nif I marched in with the others.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:34.51,0:39:35.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It'll be scary, too.}And I'm scared.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:37.59,0:39:42.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,At any rate, {I'll protect this ship \Nand the 100 million belly all the way.}I'll do anything\Nto protect this ship and the 100 million belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:42.10,0:39:45.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm counting on you... guys!}The rest is in your hands... you guys!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:47.04,0:39:49.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:52.71,0:39:57.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, this should be \Nthe place Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} was talking about.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:59.69,0:40:02.38,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Look {}here.\N{This is}{Here}That's the backstreet shopping district.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:02.38,0:40:07.60,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,You go up this canal... and here! \NUsopp is right here.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:07.60,0:40:08.93,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:08.93,0:40:13.20,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,So, Nami-san, where can we find\Nthese demoli{tion workers}shers, the Franky Family?
Dialogue: 5,0:40:14.60,0:40:16.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:16.00,0:40:17.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He isn't here?}Usopp isn't here?
Dialogue: 5,0:40:17.21,0:40:19.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you sure? Didn't you just \Nscrew up the directions?}Are you sure?\NMaybe you screwed up the directions.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:19.80,0:40:21.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not you! Keep your mouth shut!}Look who's talking, swordsmoron!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:21.77,0:40:23.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:23.40,0:40:26.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– What'd you say?! \N– {Ah, look at that}Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:29.50,0:40:31.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look! It's blood!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:31.28,0:40:34.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That idiot! He just walked off \Nwithout waiting for us!}That dumbass! \NHe shouldn't have moved!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:34.82,0:40:37.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me he...}{Do you really think he...?}He couldn't have, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:40:37.63,0:40:39.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp.
Comment: 5,0:40:40.69,0:40:48.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ahhh...}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:42.08,0:40:43.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:40:54.30,0:40:55.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:55.56,0:40:57.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:03.82,0:41:07.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! \NWhere'd you come falling from?
Dialogue: 5,0:41:08.85,0:41:10.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The shipyard...
Dialogue: 5,0:41:10.20,0:41:14.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was jumping around imitating this \None shipwright to look for Usopp.}I was copying that {guy from the shipyard}shipwright, \Njumping around to look for Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:14.28,0:41:15.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:41:15.45,0:41:16.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:16.82,0:41:19.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, guys! \NWe've got a problem!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:19.56,0:41:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp got {abducted}taken,\Nalong with the money.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:22.31,0:41:23.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:23.93,0:41:27.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on. We're on our way to their hideout.}Come on.\NWe're headed to their hideout.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:27.96,0:41:30.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp got beaten up \Nand had the money stolen from him.}They beat up Usopp and took the money.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:30.70,0:41:31.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:33.60,0:41:35.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's possible that he felt responsible}Maybe he blamed himself...
Dialogue: 5,0:41:35.53,0:41:40.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and went to pick a fight \Nwith the Franky Family all by himself.}and left all on his own \Nto confront the Franky Family.
