Dialogue: 5,0:42:04.89,0:42:09.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although he's completely \Nunconscious, he's still alive.}He's fallen unconscious; \Nhe's not dead yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:09.09,0:42:11.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He'll be okay.\NI can save him.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:16.49,0:42:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just wait a bit... Usopp.}Just rest there a moment... Usopp.
